# The Bon Pet

&gt; Singapore-based artisanal fresh pet food brand. PhD-formulated, sous vide gently cooked meals for cats and dogs. Founded 2024 by Yash and Nicolas. AVS-licensed kitchen at 26 Pioneer Crescent, Singapore 628558. AAFCO All Life Stages certified.

## About

The Bon Pet makes gently cooked fresh meals for cats and dogs in Singapore. Every recipe is formulated by PhD pet nutritionists to meet or exceed AAFCO (Association of American Feed Control Officials) nutritional standards for all life stages. Meals are cooked sous vide at 80°C to eliminate pathogens while preserving heat-sensitive nutrients like taurine, then flash-frozen and delivered cold-chain island-wide.

