## Storage &amp; feeding

- Frozen shelf life: up to 1 year from manufacture (Best Before printed on pack)
- Thawed shelf life: 2-3 days in fridge, sealed container, do not refreeze
- Serving: thaw overnight, serve at room temperature, never heat (degrades taurine)
- Adult cats baseline: 65 g × 2 meals/day (GC + ~10 g kibble)
- Kittens baseline: 65 g × 3 meals/day
- Dog portioning: based on weight and activity, see Feeding Guide
- Transition protocol: 3-5 day gradual (25% new/75% old → 50/50 → 100%)

