## Common customer questions

- Is fresh pet food worth it vs. kibble? Yes, fresh gently cooked meals retain heat-sensitive nutrients (taurine, B vitamins) that kibble extrusion destroys. More digestible, better stool quality, improved coat.
- My pet has allergies: can they eat this? Yes, all recipes are single-protein to minimise allergy risk. Kangaroo is a popular novel protein for sensitivities.
- Can I pause or cancel subscription? Yes, any time via account or WhatsApp.
- How do I transition from kibble? Gradual 3-5 day switch. Mix small portion with current food, increase ratio daily. Monitor stool.
- Do you serve all of Singapore? Yes, island-wide cold-chain delivery with 4-hour window selection.

